The paper deals with graph drawings, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG). The algorithms presented in the paper involve data structures (cs.DS) and combinatorics (cs.DM). The concept of 1-planar graphs is related to graph theory (cs.GT). Finally, the paper discusses the visibility of graphs, which is a topic in computer graphics (cs.SI).
